title: eSteem - Spotlight, top users and giveaway #16
body:

## Introduction In this series of posts, We will highlight top users of eSteem and giveaway some extra rewards. Only comments and posts stats are considered. User can only take part in one of 3 sections, either comments+posts, just posts and top earners sections and 3 leaders from each section receive rewards. We have Leaderboard feature in **Activity manager** which you can follow your progress daily in terms of staying on top among all other eSteem users and ultimately winning monthly spotlight! This is being improved in future releases to engage users of the eSteem better. ## What's eSteem Learn more about project in [eSteem FAQ post here](https://steemit.com/@good-karma/esteem-faq-updated-e2baacf0a8475) Check out my blog @good-karma for more related posts and latest announcements.
# Spotlight Congratulation to below users for being awesome top **eSteem** users! ## Top Commenters + Posters 1. @melinda010100 (2489) - 15 SBD 2. @erikah (1633) - 10 SBD 3. @cicisaja (1242) - 5 SBD ## Top Posters 1. @arie78 (470) - 15 SBD 2. @tgkluwi (452) - 10 SBD 3. @joelnoni (345) - 5 SBD ## Top Earners 1. @surfermarly (329437 vests) - 15 SBD 2. @geetharao (110019 vests) - 10 SBD 3. @jznsamuel (105061 vests) - 5 SBD
Above stats are for the last 30 days and every month there will be giveaway to top users. All you have to do is to use eSteem like you usually do! **Rewards will be sent out within 24 hours.** Checkout previous Spotlights [1](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-2017523t94140724z), [2](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-2-2017623t85513623z), [3](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-3-tggyembv2r), [4](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-4-3ca853cade3c3), [5](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-5-4dd466753a55), [6](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-6-c98e423cda1b1), [7](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-7-6151bdffbcee5), [8](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-8-e410a3b3ebd78), [9](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-9-57738f52a64c7), [10](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-10-f52afbaf23d7d), [11](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-11-6e608237d62c2), [12](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-12-5cc948020fff6), [13](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-13-9518b2a50b4a8), [14](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-14-f59b1df7943b4est), [15](https://steemit.com/esteem/@good-karma/esteem-spotlight-top-users-and-giveaway-15-cdc0a00b6c153est) Thank you for everyone for using eSteem and continuing to report bugs and suggestions with [Utopian](https://utopian.io/project/eSteemApp/esteem/github/63218416/all), we are closely following suggestions and reports there. ### Download eSteem Mobile for Android and iOS today if you haven't
